abstract: "Open-source smartphone video-acquisition suite with a Windows Hub and Android client, USB or trusted-private-network transport, scheduled capture boundaries, live preview, battery telemetry, structured file transfer, lag-test diagnostics, and optional Arduino triggering of a laboratory reference system."
